# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# OPTIONAL. The app is fully functional WITHOUT any API key — the rule/scoring
# engine does all the real work (inference, conflicts, examples, debugging,
# transformations). The key below only enables an extra "tutor narrative" that
# rewrites the structured result into flowing prose using Claude.
#
# To enable it: copy this file to `.env.local` and paste your Anthropic API key.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the model used for narrative enrichment.
# Defaults to claude-haiku-4-5-20251001 (fast + cheap).
ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-haiku-4-5-20251001
